_properties.descriptionZh: 表示实体附加特征的属性值对（例如cnschema.org中没有匹配属性的产品功能或其他特性）
_properties.rdfs:comment:
A property-value pair representing an additional characteristics of the entitity, e.g. a product feature or another characteristic for which there is no matching property in cnschema.org.

Note: Publishers should be aware that applications designed to use specific cnschema.org properties (e.g. http://cnschema.org/width, http://cnschema.org/color, http://cnschema.org/gtin13, ...) will typically expect such data to be provided using those properties, rather than using the generic property/value mechanism.
_properties.rdfs:label: additionalProperty

_properties.descriptionZh: 数值之间的排序关系，表示主语等于谓语。
_properties.rdfs:comment: This ordering relation for qualitative values indicates that the subject is equal to the object.
_properties.rdfs:label: equal

_properties.rdfs:comment: This ordering relation for qualitative values indicates that the subject is greater than the object.
_properties.rdfs:label: greater

_properties.rdfs:comment: This ordering relation for qualitative values indicates that the subject is greater than or equal to the object.
_properties.rdfs:label: greaterOrEqual

_properties.rdfs:comment: This ordering relation for qualitative values indicates that the subject is lesser than the object.
_properties.rdfs:label: lesser

_properties.rdfs:comment: This ordering relation for qualitative values indicates that the subject is lesser than or equal to the object.
_properties.rdfs:label: lesserOrEqual

_properties.descriptionZh: 定性值的序关系：表示主语不等于宾语
_properties.rdfs:comment: This ordering relation for qualitative values indicates that the subject is not equal to the object.
_properties.rdfs:label: nonEqual

_properties.descriptionZh: 指向提供关于原始值的附加信息，例如： 参考温度。
_properties.rdfs:comment: A pointer to a secondary value that provides additional information on the original value, e.g. a reference temperature.
_properties.rdfs:label: valueReference

_pTree.descriptionZh: 定性地描述一个物品的属性，比如衣服的尺寸有S，M，L和XL等等。
_pTree.rdfs:comment: A predefined value for a product characteristic, e.g. the power cord plug type 'US' or the garment sizes 'S', 'M', 'L', and 'XL'.
_pTree.rdfs:label: QualitativeValue

_properties.descriptionZh: 该项的一个附加类型， 通常用于从外部词典中向微数据语法添加更加具体的类型。它表示事物和事物本身所属的类之间的关系。在RDFa语法中, 对多类型最好使用‘typeof’属性这样的本地RDFa语法. Schema.org 工具对额外类型的理解较弱，特别是外部定义的额外类型。
_properties.rdfs:comment: An additional type for the item, typically used for adding more specific types from external vocabularies in microdata syntax. This is a relationship between something and a class that the thing is in. In RDFa syntax, it is better to use the native RDFa syntax - the 'typeof' attribute - for multiple types. Schema.org tools may have only weaker understanding of extra types, in particular those defined externally.
_properties.rdfs:label: additionalType

  bread.

  Cook time: 1 hour
  Yield: 1 loaf
  Tags: Low fat
  
    Nutrition facts:

    9 grams fat
  
  Ingredients:

  - 1 egg
  - 3/4 cup of sugar

  the flour last. Pour the mixture into a loaf pan and bake for one hour.
